Look.

241
00:14:08,680 --> 00:14:10,800
What did you buy?

242
00:14:11,720 --> 00:14:12,600
What is it?

243
00:14:14,000 --> 00:14:16,920
These are your favorite mooncakes
from Guangmingcun.

244
00:14:19,040 --> 00:14:22,840
I checked out a company today.

245
00:14:23,560 --> 00:14:24,720
What company?

246
00:14:24,800 --> 00:14:26,480
Health supplements or bed frames?

247
00:14:28,000 --> 00:14:29,840
Am I that stupid?

248
00:14:32,560 --> 00:14:33,960
I signed you up for this.

249
00:14:34,040 --> 00:14:35,880
AISI MARRIAGE COMPANY

250
00:14:36,920 --> 00:14:38,320
What is that, Mom?

251
00:14:38,960 --> 00:14:40,960
