254
00:14:45,200 --> 00:14:47,320
People basically use dating agencies.

255
00:14:47,400 --> 00:14:48,880
That's why

256
00:14:48,960 --> 00:14:50,360
I especially

257
00:14:50,440 --> 00:14:53,240
went and checked that company.

258
00:14:53,760 --> 00:14:56,000
